            <title>Description</title>
            <paragraph><strong>MarginContainer</strong> adds an adjustable margin on each side of its child controls. The margins are added around all children, not around each individual one. To control the <strong>MarginContainer</strong>'s margins, use the <literal>margin_*</literal> theme properties listed below.</paragraph>
